description.text: A function that takes in a RequestContext and returns a promise (typically, just the result of "context.sync()"). The context parameter facilitates requests to the OneNote application. Since the Office add-in and the WoOneNote application run in two different processes, the request context is required to get access to the OneNote object model from the add-in.
